cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.NE 

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with natural language processing and sentence representation learning. The use of neural networks also suggests that it could belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper's focus on text coherence and understanding could also place it in cs.CV (Computer Vision) as it deals with understanding visual scenes, and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) as it uses neural networks for learning.
